name: Internet Marketing Agency
tag_list: marketing, advertising, online-media, search-marketing, web-design, search-engine-optimization, search-engine-marketing, web-site-development
overview:
Internet Marketing Agency is a full service advertising and internet marketing agency.

Our team is made up of creative strategists and marketers working with and alongside software engineers and developers to create Web sites and applications with a focus on usability and the user experience.

We are a cross-disciplined team of strategists, developers and creative marketing professionals with a focus in Web and new media communications. We provide a holistic, integrated approach combining expert marketing and visual design with best practices for usability, search engine optimization and Web development.
